title: D:S-vol.1 Compilation (Balkan industrial)
description:
DS:vol.1 is a compilation of ExYu industrial/gothic/darkwave bands. ExYu is a region in Balkans (Europe) where former Yugoslavia was. This compilation is the first DS established and there will be more releases. You can find more info about these bands and DS at: http://www.darksceneforum.co.nr
